'''Romeo Treblanc's private viewing box''' in [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] [[Galaxies Opera House/Legends|Galaxies Opera House]] was adjacent to [[Palpatine's private viewing box|that]] of [[Supreme Chancellor/Legends|Supreme Chancellor]] [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]].

==History==
At the time of the [[Squid Lake/Legends|''Squid Lake'']] performance just prior to the end of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], [[Romeo Treblanc]], [[Tannon Praji/Legends|Tannon Praji]], [[Ottegru Grey]], [[Onara Kuat]], used this viewing box. Romeo himself was flanked by two women.

==Behind the scenes==
This viewing box is full of important [[Industrial Light & Magic]] employees. The ''[[What's The Story?]]'' feature of [[Hyperspace: The Official Star Wars Fan Club|''Hyperspace'']] has identified some of their characters.

